    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551640/extras/ebbae82fc4dd9f2909f2bfaba976c630.avif?t=1749284235\" width=616 height=72 /></span>著名于世的寻宝猎人莱昂纳多·珀瓦尔于多年前离世。虽然发掘的大部分宝物都被强盗掠夺一空，但他留下了一系列关于传说之宝的谜题——传言只有如他一般的伟大猎人才能找到。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >舞，一个看似普通但一直憧憬宝藏与冒险的女孩，终于如愿以偿前往了到处都是寻宝者和强盗的世界——那里的居民都像她一样痴迷寻宝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她本想和好朋友健一结伴前往新世界探索，但可惜的是，他们的对头拓也一同来了。更糟的是，拓也在前往异世界的途中获得了神秘力量，并决定与邪恶势力联手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >异世界中满是魔法物种，无论是雪人还是神都有可能威胁到舞的旅程。舞是会梦想成真，还是会完败于敌方势力？击败来者，解开谜题，找到传说之宝！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551640/extras/514d5d901914c8cbc145aac6e7ac2abe.avif?t=1749284235\" width=616 height=73 /></span>每种武器都会带来战斗可用的新能力，使用不同的状态效果和战斗策略击败敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索解谜，获得更强大的武器和物品。但要注意：虽然Boss的战力固定，但普通敌人会像舞一样成长变强！如果不制定好策略，光是简单的刷任务可不足以获胜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551640/extras/a0e49945e660d9a19b0c49d195b998b7.avif?t=1749284235\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551640/extras/3f0786cfd4a3ea8ca72d233e8f9c6875.avif?t=1749284235\" width=616 height=275 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551640/extras/a24b188a5512dda11b7cf3cc2e51694b.avif?t=1749284235\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551640/extras/627a8e6f3c013c0e84edcf4ea17f1fd0.avif?t=1749284235\" width=616 height=73 /></span><strong>探索世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >广阔的世界中有多种冒险可供选择，无论是喜剧悲剧，都是自己的选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不同分支</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是顽强地咬牙清除所有障碍，还是选择躺平接受拓也的帮助……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全始全终</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作中共有10个结局，从肝胆欲碎到皆大欢喜——走最好的路才能得到真正的结局。</p>",
